{"tid":2215702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【學界之恥】珠海學院教授關偉：政府應向記者發牌","createTime":"2020-09-24T07:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T07:09:03.000Z","uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"33fd9039d53c68f6f34ff342b7470be0f8ed05a4","tid":2215702,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T07:09:03.000Z","msg":"全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=406717&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406717%26home%3D1&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=8e4ddc6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406717%26home%3D1&h=4d478460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=406717&amp;home=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jcm.chuhai.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/%E9%97%9C%E5%81%89-R1-1024x803.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjcm.chuhai.edu.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%2581%2589-R1-1024x803.jpg&h=5936e781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n珠海學院新聞及傳播學系專業應用教授關偉：<br />\n「用警方的定義來做其實是太寬鬆，嚴格來說，我覺得應該要發牌給每個說自己是記者的，要拿資料去證實記者的身分很重要。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}